{"tid":597952,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"為控製成本 LG G7將用LCD屏取代OLED屏","createTime":"2018-03-19T06:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T15:38:01.000Z","uid":47132,"like":29,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"08954387d84c4fa4aa7ec23ba570ee70cb962b5c","tid":597952,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:04:58.000Z","msg":"據外媒報導，韓國市場分析師預測，LG下一代旗艦G7將會採用LCD屏幕，這主要是考慮到成本的原因。據稱，OLED屏幕的價格是相應的LCD屏幕的兩倍到三倍。<br />\n<br />\n雖然目前主流廠商都開始大規模採用OLED屏幕，LG G7仍堅持採用LCD屏幕也不會讓我們大感意外，因為之前的G系列旗艦一直都用的是LCD屏幕。不過，由於LG V30採用了OLED屏幕，因此一些用戶期待LG G7也能用上OLED屏幕。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，LG G7將採用的LCD屏實際上是自主研發的MLCD+顯示屏，據說它比傳統的LCD屏幕更省電，功耗降低35%，而且亮度也更高。<br />\n<br />\n此前傳聞LG G7將採用帶劉海的異形全面屏，後置豎直雙攝和指紋識別，整體造型跟前代有明顯變化。該機預計將於4月或5月發佈，售價或達6000元。"},{"pid":"8d70b944f3f15e2b2e71298a84c20ee688ff6ba5","tid":597952,"uid":61954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"用得LCD都會出異形屏啦掛"},{"pid":"398f4d086f4c0715e8b2e5a827520073bdbb6215","tid":597952,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:29:03.000Z","msg":"終於覺醒"},{"pid":"71c9dd98cc76d7062bc276f904ddaaa78b75e2ed","tid":597952,"uid":37820,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:40:40.000Z","msg":"其實唔見得現有oled係有幾好<br />\nLcd技術成熟我仲鍾意"},{"pid":"b2a9b942ba625973d89874b66d0566bc3e55cdb5","tid":597952,"uid":137694,"like":2,"dislike":40,"score":-38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"Lcd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebf0731527367560e547a997512162c149e5125","tid":597952,"uid":26650,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"b2a9b942ba625973d89874b66d0566bc3e55cdb5","tid":597952,"uid":137694,"like":2,"dislike":40,"score":-38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"Lcd<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm